divs: Sighting Details The Early morning of july16 , i woke up at 4h50am planing doing a day fishing trip^with my friend. Like each day i go put my dog outside and check for the newspaper. but something caught my attention just over my neighbour house. its a red white glow star like, direction west,south-west. The size of the object is 25cen coin. its the only light on sky its a cloudy sunset morning so i could see any star in sky but i see that light away. i go inside take my cam put in on night vision mode and film it for about 3-4min. then i switch on normal mode to see difference between mode, suddendly the light fade, could see nothing. i run on my backyard with a large view north, north east. after 20-30sec off scanning the sky my ufo show back from a cloud become very bright only white this time.start moving up on the other cloud for hiding with a strange pattern a helicopter or plane cant do. i see nothing after that. with my job am doing about flying each year on chopper like Astar, md530 its not what i saw. if Someone around have seeing the same object please report it. its same to be all on north east cost.

Summary: Star-like ufo show up early before sunrise
